<br>
This is a summary of the Warrior epic quest for Blade of Tactics, Blade of Strategy and the Jagged Blade of War.<br>
<br>
Quest Start<br>
<br>
Talk to Kargek Redblade and Wenden in East Freeport to start the quest.<br>
<br>
Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Swim to the Flame Tower Island, then swim underwater and find the tunnel going underneath the island. <br>
Pick up the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>
Obtain a Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth. <br>
Give the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt, Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth to Wenden to get the Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>
<br>
<br>
Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to Timorous Deep. Go to the Chessboard Island. <br>
Pick up the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt that is at the Chessboard. <br>
Go to Plane of Fear. Kill Fright, Dread or Terror to get the Ball of Everliving Golem. <br>
Go to Dreadlands. Kill all the giants at the castle until the Mountain Giant Patriarch spawns. <br>
Kill the Mountain Giant Patriarch to get the Giant Monocle. <br>
Go to Frontier Mountains. Give the Giant Monocle to Mentrax Mountainbone in the giant fort to get the Rejesium Ore. <br>
Go to East Freeport. Give the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt, Ball of Everliving Golem and Rejesium Ore to Wenden to get the Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt. <br>
<br>
<br>
Ancient Sword Blade [First]<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to Ocean of Tears. Talk to Denken Strongpick and he tells you the items he wants. <br>
Go to almost any merchant selling alcoholic beverages to buy a Keg of Vox Tail Ale. <br>
Go to Permafrost. Kill the Ice Giants to get a Block of Perma Frost. <br>
Obtain two Rebreathers from any player Tinkerer. <br>
Go to Ocean of Tears. Give the Keg of Vox Tail Ale, Block of Perma Frost and two Rebreathers to Denken Strongpick to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>
<br>
<br>
Ancient Sword Blade [Second]<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to Chardok. Kill the queen to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>
<br>
<br>
The Red Scabbard<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to East Freeport. Talk to Kargak Redblade. Say "I will do you a favor" to get the letter. <br>
Go to The Ferrott. Give the letter to Oknoggin to get the Tiny Lute. <br>
Go to East Freeport. Give the Tiny Lute to Kargak Redblade to get the book. <br>
Go to Highpass Hold. Give the book to Tenal Redblade to get the Frozen War Totem. <br>
Go to Permafrost. Kill the Goblin Wizards to get the Frozen Goblin Heart. <br>
Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Frozen War Totem and Frozen Goblin Heart to Tenal Redblade to get the Totem of Fiery War. <br>
Go to Emerald Jungle. Kill Severlious to get the Green Dragon Scale. <br>
Kill either Nagafin [SolB,] Ragefire [SolB,] or Talendor [Skyfire] to get the Red Dragon Scale. <br>
Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Totem of Fiery War, Green Dragon Scale and Red Dragon Scale to Tenal Redblade to get the Mark of the Sword. <br>
Go to Plane of Hate. Kill Maestro to get his hand. <br>
Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Mark of the Sword and Maestro's hand to Tenal Redblade to get another note. <br>
Go to Plane of Sky. Kill the Spiroc Lord to get the Spiroc Wingblade. <br>
Go to East Freeport. Give the note and Spiroc Wingblade to Kargek Redblade to get the Red Scabbard, along with instuctions on how to combine the swords. <br>
